      <description>
          &lt;p&gt;While I had other plans for this week‚Äôs post, work and exploring Vancouver didn&amp;rsquo;t really allow for any kind of preparation. It‚Äôs my first time on the Canadian west coast and while I‚Äôm sad that I‚Äôve missed this year‚Äôs FOSDEM, I enjoyed Vancouver &lt;em&gt;a lot&lt;/em&gt;! A detailed post will follow in the next couple of weeks but I definitely need to at least share some pictures with you!&lt;/p&gt;
